  "plot": [
    {
      "plot_summary": "The Doctor and Romana visit Professor Chronotis at St. Cedd's College, where they discover a dangerous Time Lord book is missing. As Skagra seeks Salyavin to control the minds of the universe, they must find the book and protect Shada. Despite being incomplete due to strikes, Shada was completed with animation and links, centered around stopping Skagra's plans using technology and mind control."
